Authorities say the car was spotted by passersby when it caught alight. JOHANNESBURG Police in Naturena in the south of Johannesburg are urging anyone who may have a missing family member to come forward and identify a man who was discovered burnt beyond recognition in the boot of a car.Authorities say the car was spotted by passersby when it caught alight.The man s charred remains were later found when the fire was put out.The police s Mavela Masondo says: We have so far opened a case of murder and an investigation is continuing. We don t know what's the motive behind the murder and we re still trying to get all information regarding the car. (Edited by Leeto M Khoza)